oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: McPhail Cliffe Office
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of an office building used by Dr. Daniel McPhail and Dr. Daniel Cliffe located on East Main Street. It was built around 1815. At one time the Heritage Foundation of Williamson County used it as an office.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Office buildings
